<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<link href="~/Content/Site.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <title>主页 - CloudX - Connect Everything!</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <script>
        window.onload = function () {
            var oDiv = document.getElementById("navitem");
            var oLi = oDiv.getElementsByTagName("li");
            for(var i = 0;i < oLi.length;i++)
            {
                oLi[i].onmouseover = function () {
                    this.style.background = "url(../Images/nav.png)";
                };
                if (i != 0)
                {
                    oLi[i].onmouseout = function () {
                        this.style.backgroundImage = "none";
                }
                };
            }
        }
        
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="body">
        <div id="navwrap">
            <div id="logowrap">
                <div id="logo"></div>
                <li id="homepage">CloudX</li>
            </div>
            <div id="navigation">
                <ul id="navitem">
                    <li id="first_li">
                        @Html.ActionLink("主页", "Index", "Home")
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        @Html.ActionLink("反馈","Feedback","Home")
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        @Html.ActionLink("联系我们","Contact","Home")
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        @Html.ActionLink("开放平台","Platform","Home")
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="download">
            <div id="picture"></div>
            <div id="description"></div>
            <div id="download_button">下载</div>
        </div>
        <div id="display">
            <div id="first_floor">
                <div id="first_floor_description">
                    <h3>
                        屏幕共享<br />
                        <h4>
                            设备太远看不见？<br />
                            一切尽在你眼中！<br />
                        </h4>
                    </h3>
                    <p> 设备之间可共享屏幕和适配<br />实现远程操作<br /><br />不同的设备还可整合起来<br />使之相互作为屏幕的扩展</p>
                </div>
                <div id="first_floor_image"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="second_floor">
                <div id="second_floor_image"></div>
                <div id="second_floor_description">
                    <h3>
                        文件资源共享<br />
                        <h4>
                            不用数据线不用找电脑<br />
                            小手机也可看大片<br />
                        </h4>
                        在PC、笔记本等储设备中适当划分出部分存储空间<br />用于储存共享的数据<br /><br />小容量的移动设备就可以随时访问到更多的资源。
                    </h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="third_floor">
                <div id="third_floor_description">
                    <h3>
                        多设备操作映射<br />
                        <h4>
                            控制电脑<br />
                            手机操作更方便<br />
                        </h4>
                    </h3>
                    <p>移动设备为传统的PC提供丰富多样的操作形式<br />当移动设备连接到家庭云中时<br /><br />可以利用设备自身的触摸屏<br />以及其他传感器来控制电脑</p>
                </div>
                <div id="third_floor_image"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="signature">
            <p>CloudX项目组©2013-2014</p>
        </div>
        @{Layout="../Shared/_Layout.cshtml";}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
